events.text: Mamadou N'Diaye made a game-winning basket at the buzzer in a 92-90 win over the Magic.
Manu Ginóbili made a game-winning free throw with no time on the clock in a 104-103 win over the Nets.
The Supersonics traded Desmond Mason to the Nets for Lucious Harris, a 2003 1st round pick (@ShDw47 Nets), and a 2003 2nd round pick (@ShDw47 Nets).
Steve Francis had 12 points, 10 rebounds and 11 assists in an 87-85 win over the Mavericks.
Rodney White made a game-winning basket with 14.3 seconds remaining in a 78-77 win over the Hawks.
Andre Miller made a game-winning free throw with no time on the clock in a 90-89 win over the Lakers.
Paul Pierce had 18 points, 12 rebounds and 12 assists in a 104-84 win over the Knicks.
Tracy McGrady had 29 points, 10 rebounds and 10 assists in a 90-79 win over the Supersonics.
Morris Peterson made a game-winning basket with 5 seconds remaining in a 99-97 win over the Trailblazers.
Damon Jones made a game-winning basket with 11.3 seconds remaining in an 88-87 win over the Pelicans.
Darius Miles made a game-winning basket at the buzzer in an 81-80 win over the Rockets.
